38 void getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(geometry_msgs::Quaternion orientation, double& roll,double& pitch, double& yaw)
39 {
40  tf::Quaternion quat;
41  tf::quaternionMsgToTF(orientation,quat);
42  quat.normalize();
43  tf::Matrix3x3 mat(quat);
44  mat.getRPY(roll, pitch,yaw);
45 }
